---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTASection from '../../components/CTASection.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Logistics Reporting Automation | Case Study"
  description="How automated reporting saved a logistics company 15+ hours per week on manual report preparation."
>
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="mb-8">
        <span class="text-sm font-medium text-brand-blue bg-brand-blue-pale px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Demo Project</span>
        <span class="ml-2 text-sm text-slate-light">Automation</span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate">Logistics Reporting Automation</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-xl text-slate-light">
        Automated multi-source report preparation, reducing weekly reporting time from 15+ hours to 15 minutes of review.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 p-4 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-sm text-amber-800">
          <strong>Note:</strong> This is a demo project illustrating typical automation outcomes. Results vary by data quality and implementation scope.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 prose prose-lg max-w-none text-slate-light">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate">The Challenge</h2>
        <p>
          A regional logistics company was spending 15+ hours per week on manual reporting. The operations team pulled data from multiple sources—their TMS, Excel spreadsheets, and email updates—to compile weekly performance reports for management.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Data scattered across 5+ systems</li>
          <li>Manual copy-paste between spreadsheets</li>
          <li>Reports often delayed or inconsistent</li>
          <li>Operations team spending Monday mornings on admin, not operations</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate mt-12">The Solution</h2>
        <p>
          We built a Python-based automation pipeline that:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Connects to all data sources via APIs and scheduled exports</li>
          <li>Consolidates and validates data automatically</li>
          <li>Generates formatted reports on a schedule</li>
          <li>Delivers reports to stakeholders via email</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate mt-12">Typical Results</h2>
        <div class="not-prose grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-6">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-success">15+ hrs</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-slate-light mt-1">Saved per week</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-success">15 min</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-slate-light mt-1">Review time only</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate mt-12">Key Takeaways</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Automation works best when processes are already defined (even if manual)</li>
          <li>Starting with high-frequency, high-effort tasks delivers fastest ROI</li>
          <li>Building in validation steps catches errors that manual processes missed</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTASection
    title="Want results like this?"
    description="Book a discovery call to identify your highest-impact automation opportunities."
  />
</BaseLayout>
